language Essence 1.3

given n, k : int(1..)
given edges : set of set (size 2) of int(1..n)

find colouring : matrix indexed by [int(1..n), int(1..k)] of int(0..1)

such that
    forAll vertex : int(1..n) .
        (sum colour : int(1..k) . colouring[vertex, colour]) = 1,
    forAll v1 : int(1..n) . forAll v2 : int(v1+1..n) .
        ({v1, v2} in edges) ->
            (forAll colour : int(1..k) .
                colouring[v1, colour] + colouring[v2, colour] <= 1)
